data.text: @etnow @AprilDRyan I’d love a job @Traderjoe Good job w/good benefits...I’m not understanding the angle of the GOP on this one. What am I missing?
@etnow He will make a come back... stay strong💪🏼
@etnow @AprilDRyan I hope he sees all the people supporting him.  The man is working and making a living and there is nothing wrong with that!
@etnow Not everyone in television makes big bucks.

@etnow Why is doing a good honest work to put food on the table and roof over your head, something to be ashamed of? The people who took the picture of him and put it on line for others to make fun off, are the ones who should  be ashamed of themselves!
@etnow Now, thanks to a #rude #Tweet this #patient #hardworking man, will have his #Comeback > God does work in #mysterious ways 😘

@etnow This story speaks to the REALITY of the acting profession-it's like professional athletics, a fortunate few have long profitable careers-the rest must save in the good years & have a Plan B in the lean years.
@etnow Celebrities are people too! Nothing wrong with hard, honest work. Bills don’t pay themselves.

@etnow And still we have illegals sitting on their asses getting free everything. You are an honest hardworking man. ✋🏻 highfive to you. The roles will come n go but your dignity will speak volumes about you.
@etnow No different than anyone else. We don’t get paid millions (really), and when money runs out, grown ups need a job. He’s just being responsible and human. #GeoffreyOwens
